## 48. FLASH-TURBO COGNITIVE PROTOCOL (v1.0) 🧠⚡

> **Berlaku untuk SEMUA model AI** (Gemini Flash/Pro, Claude Sonnet/Opus/Haiku, GPT, DeepSeek, Qwen) — tanpa pengecualian.
> Filosofi: "Oprek ECU, bukan ganti mesin" — paksa penalaran terstruktur sebelum eksekusi.

### 48.1 4-PHASE REASONING PIPELINE (MANDATORY)
Setiap request yang melibatkan perubahan kode WAJIB melewati pipeline ini:

1. **🔍 ANALYZE**: Pecah masalah → sub-komponen. Identifikasi ambiguitas, edge case, asumsi. Map file yang terdampak.
2. **🧠 REASON**: Step-by-step reasoning eksplisit. Evaluasi minimal 2 strategi solusi. Pertimbangkan: performance, security, UX.
3. **✅ VALIDATE**: Self-correction — cek bias dan logical fallacy. Cross-reference dengan `.cursorrules`, PRD, `WORKSPACE_MAP.md`. Security scan: JWT, env, RLS.
4. **🚀 EXECUTE**: Tulis kode concise dan high-performance. Surgical fix only — minimal blast radius. Sertakan verification checklist.

### 48.2 MODULAR MENTAL SKILLS (Context-Triggered)
Aktivasi "mental tool" berdasarkan konteks:

| Trigger | Mental Skill | Focus |
|---|---|---|
| Bug, error log | **[Debugging]** | Rubber ducking, edge case, stack trace |
| Contract, env, auth | **[Security]** | JWT, env leak, RLS, EIP-191 |
| UI/UX, layout | **[UI/UX]** | Native+ compliance, glassmorphism, micro-animations |
| Database, XP, sync | **[Data Integrity]** | fn_increment_xp, point_settings, view sync |
| Deploy, git | **[DevOps]** | Clean tree, gitleaks, bundle guard |
| Refactor, architecture | **[Architect]** | Composition patterns, hook extraction, SoC |

### 48.3 QUALITY ANCHORING & ANTI-LAZY GUARD
- Standar output: **SOTA** — "Apakah ini layak ditulis Staff Engineer di Google/Meta?"
- 🚫 DILARANG memberikan jawaban template/placeholder tanpa implementasi nyata.
- 🚫 DILARANG mengirim kode tanpa melalui Phase 1-3.
- 🚫 DILARANG "buru-buru jawab" — kedalaman penalaran > kecepatan respons.
- ✅ WAJIB menunjukkan reasoning trace (bahkan singkat) sebelum kode.

### 48.4 MCP-AS-SENSORY-EXTENSION
- DILARANG menebak state repositori atau database. Gunakan MCP (GitHub, Supabase) untuk membaca state aktual.
- Context window besar = kekuatan. Inject dokumentasi lengkap ke context saat diperlukan.
- RAG-like behavior: **cari tahu dulu, baru jawab**.

